snippet.title: Best Friends (2002) - Short Retro Gameplay
snippet.description:
In this video I play Best Friends from 2002. It is a 3D game made by Retro64.  The reason I put this video was for historic purposes. This game I ran on Windows XP Professional with Service Pack 1 in a VM.
